room_title: Escape room "Brains vs. Braun" by Puzzle over This in Ocean City
room_address: 10445 Old Ocean City Blvd Unit 1, Berlin, MD 21811
room_description: The players are split into two groups. Your goal is to escape your room before the other team escapes theirs. This is a highly competitive game that matches wits against warriors. Can your team outsmart the other team and escape your room and claim full bragging rights?
